text: Football Club des Girondins de Bordeaux (; commonly referred to as Girondins de Bordeaux or simply Bordeaux) is a French women's football club based in the city of Bordeaux. It has been the women's section of FC Girondins de Bordeaux since 2015. The club currently plays in the Division 1 Féminine, the highest division of women's football in France. ==Players== ===Current squad=== ==References== ==External links== * Category:Women's football clubs in France Category:Division 1 Féminine clubs Category:FC Girondins de Bordeaux
